    "sub_sektor": "Auto & Truck Dealerships",
    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Autopedia Sukses Lestari Tbk engages in the auction of two and four-wheeled vehicles under the BidWin brand name in Indonesia and internationally. The company is also involved in the retail sale of new and used cars, including vehicles comprising ambulances, caravans, minibuses, firetrucks, lorries, trailers, semi-trailers, and various other motorized transport vehicles; and retail sale of used motorcycles, such as bicycles or mopeds. In addition, it engages in the publishing of software; operation of commercial purpose web portals and/or digital platforms; and provision of business consulting and brokerage services, as well as pawning services. The company was formerly known as PT Adi Sarana Lelang and changed its name to PT Autopedia Sukses Lestari Tbk in September 2021. The company was founded in 2013 and is headquartered in Jakarta Selatan, Indonesia. PT Autopedia Sukses Lestari Tbk operates as a subsidiary of PT Adi Sarana Armada Tbk.",
